room_title: Escape room "Calico Jack's Lost Treasure" by Xtreme Escape Game in Marco Island
room_address: 909 North Collier Boulevard, Marco Island, FL 32084
room_description:
All hands on deck!
You have been captured by Calico Jack's crew off the coast of the 10,000 Islands. 
You are being held captive on his Pirate Ship.
Somewhere on the ship there is a long lost treasure.  Finding it will set you free.
You only have 60 minutes before it's time fer ye to walk the plank!
